[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 8053,
        "end_time": 11023,
        "text": "Imagine you&#39;re asked\nto invent something new."
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11023,
        "end_time": 12694,
        "text": "It could be whatever you want"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12694,
        "end_time": 14634,
        "text": "made from anything you choose"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 14634,
        "end_time": 17455,
        "text": "in any shape or size."
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 17455,
        "end_time": 21315,
        "text": "That kind of creative freedom\nsounds so liberating, doesn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 21315,
        "end_time": 23007,
        "text": "Or does it?"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 23007,
        "end_time": 27110,
        "text": "If you&#39;re like most people,\nyou&#39;d probably be paralyzed by this task."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 27110,
        "end_time": 30395,
        "text": "Without more guidance,\nwhere would you even begin?"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 30395,
        "end_time": 34625,
        "text": "As it turns out, boundless freedom\nisn&#39;t always helpful."
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 34625,
        "end_time": 38639,
        "text": "In reality, any project is restricted\nby many factors,"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 38639,
        "end_time": 39785,
        "text": "such as the cost,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 39785,
        "end_time": 42035,
        "text": "what materials you have at your disposal,"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 42035,
        "end_time": 44935,
        "text": "and unbreakable laws of physics."
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 44935,
        "end_time": 47615,
        "text": "These factors are called \ncreative constraints,"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 47615,
        "end_time": 49838,
        "text": "and they&#39;re the requirements \nand limitations"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 49838,
        "end_time": 54236,
        "text": "we have to address \nin order to accomplish a goal."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 54236,
        "end_time": 57066,
        "text": "Creative constraints apply \nacross professions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 57066,
        "end_time": 58876,
        "text": "to architects and artists,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 58876,
        "end_time": 59774,
        "text": "writers,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 59774,
        "end_time": 60713,
        "text": "engineers,"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 60713,
        "end_time": 62736,
        "text": "and scientists."
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 62736,
        "end_time": 65586,
        "text": "In many fields, constraints play\na special role"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 65586,
        "end_time": 69056,
        "text": "as drivers of discovery and invention."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 69056,
        "end_time": 71657,
        "text": "During the scientific process \nin particular,"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 71657,
        "end_time": 75646,
        "text": "constraints are an essential part\nof experimental design."
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 75646,
        "end_time": 79766,
        "text": "For instance, a scientist studying\na new virus would consider,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 79766,
        "end_time": 83287,
        "text": "&quot;How can I use the tools \nand techniques at hand"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 83287,
        "end_time": 89069,
        "text": "to create an experiment that tells me\nhow this virus infects the body&#39;s cells?"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 89069,
        "end_time": 92768,
        "text": "And what are the limits of my knowledge\nthat prevent me"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 92768,
        "end_time": 96076,
        "text": "from understanding \nthis new viral pathway?&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 96076,
        "end_time": 99748,
        "text": "In engineering, constraints have us\napply our scientific discoveries"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 99748,
        "end_time": 103118,
        "text": "to invent something new and useful."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 103118,
        "end_time": 106706,
        "text": "Take, for example, \nthe landers Viking 1 and 2,"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 106706,
        "end_time": 111338,
        "text": "which relied on thrusters to arrive\nsafely on the surface of Mars."
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 111338,
        "end_time": 112798,
        "text": "The problem?"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 112798,
        "end_time": 116118,
        "text": "Those thrusters left foreign chemicals\non the ground,"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 116118,
        "end_time": 118778,
        "text": "contaminating soil samples."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 118778,
        "end_time": 121697,
        "text": "So a new constraint was introduced."
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 121697,
        "end_time": 124148,
        "text": "How can we land a probe on Mars"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 124148,
        "end_time": 127459,
        "text": "without introducing chemicals\nfrom Earth?"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 127459,
        "end_time": 130769,
        "text": "The next Pathfinder mission used\nan airbag system"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 130769,
        "end_time": 134159,
        "text": "to allow the rover to bounce\nand roll to a halt"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 134159,
        "end_time": 138400,
        "text": "without burning contaminating fuel."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 138400,
        "end_time": 143150,
        "text": "Years later, we wanted to send\na much larger rover: Curiosity."
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 143150,
        "end_time": 146389,
        "text": "However, it was too large \nfor the airbag design,"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 146389,
        "end_time": 149019,
        "text": "so another constraint was defined."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 149019,
        "end_time": 152689,
        "text": "How can we land a large rover\nwhile still keeping rocket fuel"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 152689,
        "end_time": 155439,
        "text": "away from the Martian soil?"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 155439,
        "end_time": 158461,
        "text": "In response, engineers had a wild idea."
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 158461,
        "end_time": 161490,
        "text": "They designed a skycrane."
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 161490,
        "end_time": 164430,
        "text": "Similar to the claw machine at toy stores,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 164430,
        "end_time": 168150,
        "text": "it would lower the rover \nfrom high above the surface."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 168150,
        "end_time": 173051,
        "text": "With each invention, the engineers\ndemonstrated an essential habit"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 173051,
        "end_time": 174711,
        "text": "of scientific thinking -"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 174711,
        "end_time": 178942,
        "text": "that solutions must recognize\nthe limitations of current technology"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 178942,
        "end_time": 181392,
        "text": "in order to advance it."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 181392,
        "end_time": 183821,
        "text": "Sometimes this progress is iterative,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 183821,
        "end_time": 187873,
        "text": "as in, &quot;How can I make a better\nparachute to land my rover?&quot;"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 187873,
        "end_time": 190512,
        "text": "And sometimes, it&#39;s innovative,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 190512,
        "end_time": 192471,
        "text": "like how to reach our goal"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 192471,
        "end_time": 196241,
        "text": "when the best possible \nparachute isn&#39;t going to work."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 196241,
        "end_time": 199692,
        "text": "In both cases, the constraints \nguide decision-making"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 199692,
        "end_time": 203351,
        "text": "to ensure we reach each objective."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 203351,
        "end_time": 206492,
        "text": "Here&#39;s another Mars \nproblem yet to be solved."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 206492,
        "end_time": 209832,
        "text": "Say we want to send astronauts\nwho will need water."
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 209832,
        "end_time": 214432,
        "text": "They&#39;d rely on a filtration system\nthat keeps the water very clean"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 214432,
        "end_time": 217766,
        "text": "and enables 100% recovery."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 217766,
        "end_time": 219970,
        "text": "Those are some pretty tough constraints,"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 219970,
        "end_time": 222993,
        "text": "and we may not have \nthe technology for it now."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 222993,
        "end_time": 225833,
        "text": "But in the process of trying \nto meet these objectives,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 225833,
        "end_time": 230801,
        "text": "we might discover other applications\nof any inventions that result."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 230801,
        "end_time": 233713,
        "text": "Building an innovative \nwater filtration system"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 233713,
        "end_time": 238204,
        "text": "could provide a solution for farmers\nworking in drought-stricken regions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 238204,
        "end_time": 243693,
        "text": "or a way to clean municipal water\nin polluted cities."
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 243693,
        "end_time": 246163,
        "text": "In fact, many scientific advances"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 246163,
        "end_time": 249494,
        "text": "have occurred when serendipitous failures\nin one field"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 249494,
        "end_time": 252475,
        "text": "address the constraints of another."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 252475,
        "end_time": 255684,
        "text": "When scientist Alexander Fleming\nmistakenly contaminated"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 255684,
        "end_time": 257705,
        "text": "a Petri dish in the lab,"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 257705,
        "end_time": 262634,
        "text": "it led to the discovery \nof the first antibiotic, penicillin."
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 262634,
        "end_time": 264585,
        "text": "The same is true of synthetic dye,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 264585,
        "end_time": 265624,
        "text": "plastic,"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 265624,
        "end_time": 267055,
        "text": "and gunpowder."
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 267055,
        "end_time": 269046,
        "text": "All were created mistakenly,"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 269046,
        "end_time": 272804,
        "text": "but went on to address the constraints\nof other problems."
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 272804,
        "end_time": 277025,
        "text": "Understanding constraints guides\nscientific progress,"
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 277025,
        "end_time": 281847,
        "text": "and what&#39;s true in science\nis also true in many other fields."
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 281847,
        "end_time": 287506,
        "text": "Constraints aren&#39;t the boundaries\nof creativity, but the foundation of it."
    }
]